601 (2008)], but provide a slightly different\nperspective via the formulation in terms of an eigenvalue problem.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 5 Nov 2010 08:47:44 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 26 Nov 2010 14:33:51 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 13 Dec 2010 08:46:30 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Fri, 4 Mar 2011 13:02:12 GMT"}],"update_date":"2011-03-07"}
