rated through zero-point\nflucturations of the Minkowski vacuum encounters a thermal bath at the\ntemperature T=\\hbar a/(2\\pi ck).\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 5 Nov 2010 15:15:30 GMT"}],"update_date":"2010-11-08"}
